  "title": "VeinDigging",
  "description": "VeinMiner for modern MC!",
  "body": "<center><img src=\"https://nyako.gay/assets/veindigging.png\"></center>\n\n# <center>VeinDigging</center>\n\n<strong>VeinDigging</strong> is a mod which allows players to VeinDig -- just like VeinMiner! This mod differs from other VeinMiner mods by being optional on the client. This means <strong>anyone on your server can VeinDig by sneaking</strong>, but people with the mod installed can use the <strong>VeinDig keybind!</strong> Additionally, you will automatically stop VeinDigging right before your tool breaks.\n\n<br>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>For server owners:</strong></span></p>\n<p>There are whitelist and blacklist tags available:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>veindigging:bind_blacklist</li>\n<li>veindigging:bind_whitelist</li>\n<li>veindigging:shift_blacklist</li>\n<li>veindigging:shift_whitelist</li>\n<li>veindigging:global_blacklist</li>\n<li>veindigging:global_whitelist</li>\n</ul>\n<p>The only whitelist on by default is the shift whitelist, which contains <strong>logs, leaves, ores and glowstone.&nbsp;</strong>This means people sneaking won't accidentally VeinDig anything they don't mean to. I'd recommend against turning the shifting whitelist off.</p>\n\n# \n\n<center>\n<a href=\"https://github.com/NyakoFox/VeinDigging/\"><img alt=\"Available on GitHub\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@intergrav/devins-badges@3/assets/cozy/available/github_vector.svg\"/></a>\n<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/veindigging\"><img alt=\"Available on CurseForge\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@intergrav/devins-badges@3/assets/cozy/available/curseforge_vector.svg\"/></a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/veindigging\"><img alt=\"Available on Modrinth\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@intergrav/devins-badges@3/assets/cozy/available/modrinth_vector.svg\"/></a>\n<br>\n<img alt=\"Available for Fabric\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@intergrav/devins-badges@3/assets/cozy/supported/fabric_vector.svg\"/>\n<img alt=\"Available for Quilt\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@intergrav/devins-badges@3/assets/cozy/supported/quilt_vector.svg\"/>\n<img alt=\"Won't support Forge\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@intergrav/devins-badges@3/assets/cozy/unsupported/forge_vector.svg\"/>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/fabric-api\"><img alt=\"Requires Fabric API\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@intergrav/devins-badges@3/assets/cozy/requires/fabric-api_vector.svg\"/></a>\n<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/cloth-config\"><img alt=\"Requires Cloth Config API\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@intergrav/devins-badges@3/assets/cozy/requires/cloth-config-api_vector.svg\"/></a>\n\n#\n\n<a href=\"https://ko-fi.com/nyakofox\"><img alt=\"Support us on Ko-fi\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@intergrav/devins-badges@3/assets/cozy/donate/kofi-plural_vector.svg\"/></a><a href=\"https://patreon.com/nyakofox\"><img alt=\"Support us on Patreon\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@intergrav/devins-badges@3/assets/cozy/donate/patreon-plural_vector.svg\"/></a>\n\n</center>\n\n**Supporters get early releases of my mods, as well as special perks and credits in my mods.**\n\n*As I am a solo developer who is unfit for work, any help would be appreciated. 🩷*\n",
